{"article_id":"BxRwChVjawFm2ed7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"JOINT BASE","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"ANDREWS , Maryland -","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"President Donald Trump welcomed home three Americans","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"freed by North Korea","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"early Thursday","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"and declared","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"their release was a step toward his de-nuclearizing the Korean Peninsula .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"The prisoners were freed","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"after Secretary of State Mike Pompeo traveled to the North Korean capital","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"and met with leaders ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"including dictator Kim Jong Un .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"A giant America flag was suspended between two fire trucks on the edge of the taxiway .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"President Trump and the first lady boarded the plane","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"before the men stepped out ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"shaking hands with the president","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and waving .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Watch","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"as the 3 freed Americans from North Korea arrive at Andrews Air Force Base","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"The men are Korean-American missionary Kim Dong-chul ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"detained in 2015","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"and sentenced in 2016 to 10 years ' hard labor .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Kim Sang-duk ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"also known as Tony Kim ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"who spent a month teaching at the foreign-funded Pyongyang University of Science and Technology","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"before he was arrested in 2017 ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"along with Kim Hak-song ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"who also taught at PUST","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and was detained last year .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"The three had earlier given their thanks in a statement","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"released by the State Department","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"as their plane stopped over in Alaska .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"`` We would like to express our deep appreciation to the United States government , President Trump , Secretary Pompeo , and the people of the United States","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"for bringing us home , ''","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"the men said .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"`` We thank God , and all our families and friends","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"who prayed for us and for our return .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"God Bless America , the greatest nation in the world . ''","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"A White House spokeswoman said","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"the three former prisoners would be taken to Walter Reed National Military Medical Center in nearby Maryland for further medical evaluation .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"`` Frankly we did n't think","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"it was going to happen","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and it did , ''","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"President Trump said","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"after thanking Kim","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"for releasing the men .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"`` We 're starting off on a new footing .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"This is a wonderful thing","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"that he released the folks early . ''","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"we have a very good chance","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"of doing something very meaningful , ''","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"Trump said .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"`` My proudest achievement will be","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"- this is part of it -","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"when we denuclearize that entire peninsula . ''","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"The president said","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"a date and location has now been set for his historic summit with Kim .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"Sources tell News","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"it will likely happen in the next few weeks in Singapore .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Just before wrapping up ,","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"the president did take time to remember Otto Warmbier , the American college student","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"who was imprisoned and tortured by North Korea","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"and died shortly after his release .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"`` His parents have become friends of ours ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"said President Trump .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"`` They are spectacular people","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"and I just want to pay my respects . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":133,"left":0,"right":132,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":1,"right":131,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":131,"left":92,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":80,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":71,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":69,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":68,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":68,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":79,"left":75,"right":78,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":7,"right":73,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":8,"right":72,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":12,"right":77,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":77,"left":13,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":91,"left":81,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"par